title: Internal compiler error: unexpected panic

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

labels.name: ICEBreaker-Cleanup-Crew
labels.description: Helping to "clean up" bugs with minimal examples and bisections

body:

```

git checkout 6959e702ee7833328176bc7532dae65517b390fa
cargo build
```

```
commit-date: 2021-03-24
host: x86_64-apple-darwin
release: 1.53.0-nightly
LLVM version: 12.0.0
```
